-- French President Sarkozy’s Son Hospitalized in Ukrainian Resort
-- B y   D a r y n a   K r a s n o l u t s k a
-- 2012-01-25T14:05:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-25/french-president-sarkozy-s-son-hospitalized-in-ukrainian-resort.html
Pierre Sarkozy, son of French
President  Nicolas Sarkozy , has been hospitalized in Ukraine’s
Black Sea resort of Odessa after feeling ill, said Anna
Osipchuk, a spokeswoman for the city’s mayor.  Pierre Sarkozy, who had planned to perform as a DJ at a
party, became ill as he traveled yesterday to Ukraine from
Prague in the  Czech Republic  and was hospitalized on arrival,
Osipchuk said today by phone from Odessa, adding that the city’s
mayor has visited him in the morning.  “He’s now feeling much better and is preparing for his
departure home,” Osipchuk said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Daryna Krasnolutska in Kiev at 
 dkrasnolutsk@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Balazs Penz at 
 bpenz@bloomberg.net . 